<i>noun</i>: 절약 [저략], 보전 [보ː전], 보수 [보ː수] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>절약 [저략]</dt><br>
<dd>savings; reduction; conservation</dd><br>
<dd>마구 쓰지 않고 꼭 필요한 데에만 써서 아낌.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saving resources by refraining from reckless use and using them only when necessary.</dd><br>
<dt>보전 [보ː전]</dt><br>
<dd>preservation; conservation</dd><br>
<dd>변하는 것이 없도록 잘 지키고 유지함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of protecting and maintaining something so that it does not change.</dd><br>
<dt>보수 [보ː수]</dt><br>
<dd>conservation</dd><br>
<dd>새로운 것이나 변화를 적극적으로 받아들이기보다는 전통적인 제도나 방법을 그대로 지키려고 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of sticking to traditional systems or methods and being reluctant to accept new ones eagerly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>